{"tid":10401,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"(疑問)如何欣賞藝術？","createTime":"2016-11-29T02:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T07:48:30.000Z","uid":25718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b581a460384896b408bc011255a2095f27bbc5b","tid":10401,"uid":25718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T02:25:52.000Z","msg":"其實學術上藝術欣賞/分析(appreciation)有冇標準同定義？<br />\n何謂好？何謂有藝術價值/深度？<br />\n如有，求推薦有關嘅書同資料<br />\n藝術呢度廣義包括大部份娛樂<br />\n例如： 畫、音樂、電影、電視、動漫畫、遊戲等等<br />\n<br />\n大學嘅music/art appreciation嘅course多數只係講歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歷史我都有興趣<br />\n但係我想學 音樂/電影/動畫 評論嘅methodology<br />\n唔知點樣入手"},{"pid":"d6f987d25a80fbb3da3150b1bd7e72e32b09db8f","tid":10401,"uid":25718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"舊野1999無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c22396ba50c12bc8185b6cff9a0cf17e84d747","tid":10401,"uid":5760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:16:13.000Z","msg":"techniques?"},{"pid":"db015c1660074ca9af1d401c45fa7d36b5a4b32b","tid":10401,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:32:55.000Z","msg":"評論嘅話<br />\n不妨睇睇現今一些評論家嘅寫法<br />\n台灣 唐諾 可以一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7da2fbf808a195c2fb6d8e74b368e5dc12aa96f","tid":10401,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"同埋如果想知寫大眾評論<br />\n其實學術上嘅專書未必好有用<br />\n始終果種係比番學院睇<br />\n當然可以參考吓<br />\n同埋評價藝術無絕對嘅標準"},{"pid":"8d59e1da24168b7cc506df49de20ff2f3fac50eb","tid":10401,"uid":25718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋如果想知寫大眾評論<br />\n其實學術上嘅專書未必好有用<br />\n始終果種係比番學院睇<br />\n當然可以參考吓<br />\n同埋評價藝術無絕對嘅標準</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然無絕對標準<br />\n只係想知有冇學術上嘅標準黎參考/借鑒一下"},{"pid":"c4e7935b55c63f41dd6b29acfb4a19b30c269890","tid":10401,"uid":25718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T07:48:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>techniques?</blockquote><br />\n咩意思？<br />\n可唔可以詳細講下"}]}